{"tid":2392103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"4女學生佐敦補習遇突擊封區　一度未能離開","createTime":"2021-02-02T15:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T15:46:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40e4227a0d8cc5ab7a04a4fb337cf5a9db746bea","tid":2392103,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"在佐敦長樂街「受限區域」內的百樂大廈，今晚（2日）有4名女學生在補習後放學時適逢突擊封區而未能離開。民政總署人員安排4人先行採樣本檢測，並要求她們聯絡家長到場接送。其中一名家長到場時表示，擔心女兒沒有足夠食物及行裝而要在補習社過夜。至晚上9時半過後，在民政總署安排及准許下，警員登記家長及學生資料後，安排他們離開封鎖區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20210202/s00001/def427f5951da8326a34a5633024f5e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20210202%2Fs00001%2Fdef427f5951da8326a34a5633024f5e8.jpg&h=45203de9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af484cdf69fd3dfe2849ad0ef4e54e9d32d87a8c","tid":2392103,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"得一個女學生?"},{"pid":"b6293958c69654a5690967968334a892180594f0","tid":2392103,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"放開個學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7db53e3f57682c47ed627a3423ec2c1e2026ab4","tid":2392103,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"限聚令?"},{"pid":"28ce269194baf29299dbdbad49e31b75fed2b996","tid":2392103,"uid":199456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"好彩個D狗唔係休緊班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6327310e2e6ba64ee67d05546a546b90c8da6ce","tid":2392103,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"有排比黑警玩"},{"pid":"bbeb3ddf2f81a81faa7d7ad8530d1c5c395b40cd","tid":2392103,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"我請佢地住賓館啦<img src=\"/ass